<P>
   KOSOVO-IMMIG (New York) _ The 20,000 Kosovar refugees coming to
the United States will be given green cards that will pave the way
for them to become permanent citizens. But the decision has angered
some Albanians who say it plays into the hands of Milosevic. By
Blaine Harden.
