   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MARKET-BOOMERS (Undated) _ Market watchers increasingly are
linking an irrepressible market to one of the country's most
significant demographic trends: 75 million baby boomers saving and
investing for retirement. By Kimberly Blanton. 1500 words. GRAPHIC:
13 picas x 4 inches,``Money supply.''
</P>
