</P>
<P>
   Here is a preliminary look at the graphics scheduled for the
Sunday financial section of The Times. These graphics will be
transmitted this evening. The descriptions and sizes are tentative.
Please check tonight's late budget for stories and specific
graphics.
</P>
<P>
   BARCLAYS_Overview -- 2 x 8 -- (BC-BARCLAYS-GLOBAL-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Barclays' performance, assets and rankings.
</P>
<P>
   EUROPE_Firms overseas -- 1 x 5 1/4 -- (BC-EUROPE-BUYOUTS-NYT)
