School in Littleton.''How can you help? How can you get help?'' is
a top link on the Colorado state homepage, along with a link to
Gov. Bill Owens' pledge against gun violence in schools.The page
directs potential donors to send money to the Mile High United
Way's Community Healing Fund, offers directions to potential blood
donors to locations on the Front Range and provides a list of 14
hot-line numbers. (Grand Junction Daily Sentinel). 8.
