   NATIONAL NEWS (``a'' category)
</P>
<P>
   SCHOOL-SHOOTING (Littleton, Colo.) _ Investigators are checking
school video cameras and have traced the guns used in the Tuesday
shooting massacre at Columbine High School back to their original
owners. By ARMANDO VILLAFRANCA.
</P>
<P>
   SHOOTING-MEMORIAL (Littleton, Colo.) _ A memorial service is
held for a 16-year-old victim of the Columbine High School
shooting. By TONY FREEMANTLE.
</P>
<P>
   CRASH-VERDICT (Littleton, Colo.) _ A jury said a construction
company failed to post proper highway warnings about a traffic jam
and awarded $41 million to the families of two Colorado men killed
in a 1997 crash, as well as their friend who suffered brain damage.
By RON NISSIMOV.
</P>
