   BARCLAYS-GLOBAL (Undated) _ Look out Vanguard, or for that
matter Fidelity: The giant money manager you've never heard of,
Barclays Global Investors, is the unrivalled king of fund indexing
with more assets and lower costs than Vanguard, and nearly as much
under management as Fidelity. Now they are stepping out of the
institutional-money mists into the consumer fund business. By
Robert D. Hershey Jr.
