<P>
   ABOUT-CARS-LESABRE (Undated) _ Buick engineers have recast the
LeSabre, their big-selling, V6-engined, front-drive sedan, from the
suspension up. The LeSabre's biggest surprise is the way it rides
and handles. It rivals and in some ways improves on the smooth
competence of a Toyota Avalon and a Chrysler Concorde, two
competing cars I drove for comparison purposes. By Leonard M.
Apcar. (Moved).
