<P>
   HKN-BRUINS-THORNTON (Greensboro, N.C.) _ The ache, twinge, and
soreness around Joe Thornton's sternum, disappears. ``I'm 100
percent. . . . It will be good to be in the lineup.'' By Kevin Paul
Dupont.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-INDIANS-REDSOX (Boston) _ By Gordon Edes.
</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
<P>
   BBA-SHAUGHNESSY-COLUMN (Boston) _ By Dan Shaughnessy.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-CELTICS-BULLS (Chicago) -- By Michael Holley.
