<SLUG> BC-ELECTRIC-COMPANY-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
`ELECTRIC   COMPANY' COMES TO CABLE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY MARLA MATZER  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ Hey you guuuuuuys ... Letter Man, Easy Reader and
