F-16 WOES (Phoenix) - Luke Air Force Base officials now say a
faulty engine part that caused the crash of an F-16 in February and
perhaps a crash last month also may to blame for four more mishaps
since 1996. By JENNIFER BARRETT. Story will move in the ``F''
category. &QL; 
