</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-JOURNAL-ALBANIA-0424-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    LETTER FROM ALBANIA: UNFILING TONIGHT -- HERE'S WHY
