<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LEWIS-TRIAL-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HARRIS-LEWIS DEFENDS MEMORY OF LATE BASKETBALL STAR 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (a and s coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By SACHA PFEIFFER  
 c.1999 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   BOSTON -- Just days before the trial is to begin, the widow of
Celtics star Reggie Lewis said Friday that she had filed suit
against the doctors who treated her husband to clear his name after
a story in the Wall Street Journal suggested that cocaine use was a
factor in his death.
