<HEADLINE>
TICKETS FOR `PHANTOM MENACE' WILL BE AVAILABLE WEEK BEFORE OPENING
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
BY DAVE MCNARY  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
